<p class="indent1" style="-uslm-lc:I12" xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:dcterms="http://purl.org/dc/terms/" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance">In the case of any taxpayer who enters into a written binding contract before <date date="2010-05-01">May 1, 2010</date>, to close on the purchase of a principal residence before <date date="2010-07-01">July 1, 2010</date>, and who purchases such residence before <date date="2010-10-01">October 1, 2010</date>, paragraph (1) shall be applied by substituting “<date date="2010-10-01">October 1, 2010</date>” for “<date date="2010-05-01">May 1, 2010</date>”.</p>
